{"tid":1054561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"116歲日本阿嬤田中加子 金氏紀錄認定全球最長壽","createTime":"2019-03-10T01:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T02:08:27.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"32759244bd1b6ba19f000890ded3a07b09d19843","tid":1054561,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20190309/816916785756.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20190309%2F816916785756.jpg&h=629249e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現居日本福岡市的田中加子，今天以116歲高齡獲金氏世<br />\n界紀錄認定為全球不分男女最長壽長者，田中阿嬤開心地接下金氏世界紀錄證書。<br />\n <br />\n日本共同社報導，金氏世界紀錄相關人員今天拜訪田中阿嬤所生活的老人中心，並頒贈證書，田中阿嬤眼眶泛淚地說：「感謝。」<br />\n <br />\n福岡市長高島宗一郎也出席授證儀式，並祝福田中阿嬤「恭喜成為世界最長壽長者」，還贈予阿嬤一張祝賀狀。<br />\n <br />\n日本厚生勞動省去年7月27日表示，日本最高齡人瑞都千代22日以117歲高齡過世，住在福岡市的田中當時以115歲成為日本最高齡人瑞。<br />\n <br />\n老人中心去年表示，田中阿嬤平常都使用手推車在中心內散步，每天除了必吃3餐和點心，最近特別愛喝罐裝咖啡歐蕾，一天都要喝3到4罐。<br />\n <br />\n田中阿嬤的興趣是跟中心內其他老人玩黑白棋，並練習計算題等。"},{"pid":"9bdb4a8862e232f7a853c83f8b7af5bf819b0058","tid":1054561,"uid":63287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"供樓60年ok😅"},{"pid":"d00dc3c9e8380a3301d6c0c330b0c15ecbb5b9a0","tid":1054561,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"60歲中年"},{"pid":"087a47e26d3d2b874abdb7c79a1a3f41b96fe604","tid":1054561,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:53:59.000Z","msg":"銀氏"},{"pid":"02aa9b8fa7849b3d474e3157fa4143ccbda3e3c4","tid":1054561,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"3-4 杯咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿婆身體幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e4f49c4655db1ac8a0b6b082991531d5a7e458","tid":1054561,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:04:56.000Z","msg":"根本呢啲長壽老人係基因令到可以咁長命。"},{"pid":"8915af3126600d5c75fc893f0e7eb7204e6b6503","tid":1054561,"uid":136355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"日本環境質素咁好"},{"pid":"39e675306ef76cbcc5ee9b521cadc5630f72912b","tid":1054561,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:08:27.000Z","msg":"人生重質不重量"}]}